🌐 Name: SafeControl Panel

“Where Safe owners, signers, and automation live in perfect harmony.

📐 Layout Overview (Wireframe Concept)
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ 🛡️ SafeControl Panel                        ⚙️ Settings 🔔 │
├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Sidebar      | Main View                                    │
│──────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────│
│ 🏠 Overview   | 📊 Wallet Stats                              │
│ 🔐 Owners     | 💼 Proposals                                │
│ 🧾 History    | 🔁 Threshold Updates                        │
│ 💬 Activity   | 📥 Incoming Transactions                    │
│ 📡 Bots       | ⚙️ GitHub & Discord Automations            │
│ 📱 Extensions | 📦 Safe App Extensions                      │
│ 🔍 Search     | 🔐 MPC / Reown Signatures                   │
└──────────────┴──────────────────────────────────────────────┘

🎨 Design Style
Element
Style
Theme
Midnight (dark UI, neon accent colors like teal, purple, electric blue)
Typography
Inter, Satoshi, or Space Grotesk (clean, futuristic fonts)
Animations
Micro-animations on button hovers, proposal state changes
Icons
Phosphor / Tabler / Lucide (for clear, minimal crypto-style icons)
Security UX
Motion blur + “shield verification” animation on signer approvals

🧩 Feature Breakdown
1. 🔐 Wallet Overview Tab
	•	Current chain, Safe address, balance (ETH + tokens)
	•	Threshold + signer count
	•	🔄 Switch Safe
	•	🧠 AI Copilot Summary (GPT-powered Safe status)

2. 👥 Owners Manager
	•	Table view of owners (addresses, ENS, GitHub ID linked)
	•	Add/Remove owner w/ Safe proposal builder
	•	Owner role tagging (e.g., Approver, Delegate, Viewer)
	•	🔒 Signer status with Reown/MPC integration

3. 📥 Transaction Proposals
	•	Timeline-style view of pending + historical proposals
	•	Status: 🟢 Approved, 🟡 Pending, 🔴 Rejected
	•	“One-click sign” if signer
	•	GitHub/Discord trigger indicators
	•	🔗 Links to Etherscan/SafeTx

4. 📦 Safe App Extensions
	•	Live preview of embedded Safe Apps
	•	Warns if unofficial app used (security modal)
	•	Add new dApp via verified Safe AppKit plugins

5. ⚙️ Automation Tab
	•	GitHub bot PR trigger configs
	•	Discord webhook status
	•	Telegram/Slack integrations
	•	Auto-label Safe transactions from GitHub PRs

6. 📡 AI Copilot Panel
	•	Type: “Propose upgrade to threshold 3/5 on Arbitrum Safe”
	•	Auto-generates proposal + notifies signers
	•	Hooks into project-setup.ts logic

⸻

✨ BONUS UI/UX Features
	•	🧩 Drag-and-drop dashboard blocks
	•	🌐 Multichain badge on each Safe panel (ETH, Arbitrum, etc.)
	•	🔐 Reown Signature Bubble when a Reown key signs a proposal
	•	🎥 Lottie animations on threshold change, proposal confirmation
	•	📈 Real-time Safe health score powered by backend heuristics
	•	📳 Mobile-friendly PWA-ready design

⸻

🧪 Built With:
	•	Frontend: Next.js + TypeScript
	•	Styling: TailwindCSS + Shadcn UI + Radix UI
	•	Auth: WalletConnect, Reown, GitHub OAuth
	•	Backend: Node.js or serverless functions (Vercel/Cloudflare)
	•	Infra: GitHub Actions, Safe SDK, Reown SDK, Discord Webhooks
